<subSubSection id="C337088DF770B131B182FC7030A74089" pageId="5" pageNumber="526" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F770B131B182FC7030A74089" blockId="5.[151,1437,425,972]" pageId="5" pageNumber="526">
COMMENTS: Date and place are confirmed by journal entries. Wahlberg collected at the mouth of the uMlazi River, Durban, from 
<date id="FF937DC6F770B131B0C7FC4E30A34089" box="[386,666,945,972]" pageId="5" pageNumber="526" value="1841-03-11" valueMax="1841-05-06" valueMin="1841-03-11">11 March to 6 May 1841</date>
.
</paragraph>
